thread.title: Tom Sobb
thread.title_full: Spa Store Australia reviewed by Tom Sobb

author: Tom Sobb
title: Tom Sobb
text: I have purchased a few items from Spastore and have found the products, prices and delivery arrangements to be excellent. I would recommend to others that when seeking parts for a spa, check other products and prices with other companies. I'm sure you will agree with me that Spastore are most competitive.
